dc_title_s: Map of land-grant and bond-aided railroads of the United States
dc_description_s: Outline map of the United States showing major drainage, cities and towns, and military posts.|Bond-aided roads shown by heavy black lines. Fifty per cent land grant roads shown by red lines. Free land grant roads shown by green lines. Connections shown by light black lines.; Description derived from published bibliography.|67 x 96 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:5,000,000|General Map Collection
